reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Product Review: Studless Drywall TV Mount for 12-55 inch TVs
reviews.reviewText: Product Review: Studless Drywall TV Mount for 12-55 inch TVsI recently purchased the Studless Drywall TV Mount for my 42-inch LED TV, and I must say that I am extremely pleased with its performance. This TV wall bracket is designed specifically for drywall installations and provides a hassle-free and secure mounting solution for TVs ranging from 12 to 55 inches.One of the standout features of this TV mount is its studless design, which allows for easy installation on drywall without the need for finding and attaching to studs. This feature makes it incredibly convenient, especially if you're unsure of stud placement or if there are no studs available in your desired location. Despite the lack of studs, the mount feels rock solid and provides excellent stability for my TV.The versatility of this mount is also worth mentioning. It supports VESA patterns up to 400x400mm, making it compatible with a wide range of LED, LCD, plasma, flat, and curved screen TVs and monitors. The weight capacity of 100 lbs ensures that it can accommodate most TVs in the market without any concerns about stability or safety.Installing the mount was a breeze, thanks to the clear instructions and the included hardware. The package came with all the necessary screws, bolts, and spacers, which made the process quick and straightforward. The mount itself has a low-profile design, which means my TV sits close to the wall and looks sleek and stylish.Once the TV was mounted, I was pleased to find that the mount allows for easy tilting and swiveling. This feature is great for achieving the perfect viewing angle.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars SO EASY TO INSTALL & STURDY!
reviews.reviewText: 10/10! As someone who has no experience mounting a TV This was so easy & It worked perfectly with my 32inch little TV, instructions are super clear all you need is a hammer!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: So cheap but so simple. I've always thought that most TV mounts were so overkill. They would make sense if I was mounting a few hundred pounds to the wall. I recognize that this is a cheap chinsy product, but it gets the job done. And, it mounts as close close/tight to the wall. As long as you don't mount a TV larger than advised, you should have no worries.Make sure you've slid the TV and the mount in properly. It's easy to mistakenly think they've overlapped when it's not.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is the best and easy to install
reviews.reviewText: I was skeptical, honestly, on how well this would work but figured I would try and if my tv fell it’s a sign to get a new one. My daughter has a 65 inch tv and it was starting to make her dresser sag in the middle due to the weight. She wanted me to mount it on her wall but….I didn’t want to go through all that. Then I found this and ordered it. The price was low enough. It came with a lot of different screw sizes to fit the back of the tv. I found ones to fit perfectly and literally took about 10 minutes start to finish. Super easy and needed 2 tools. It came with a level to help. I ended up ordering another for my other daughter’s 65 inch tv. I would absolutely recommend getting this. I am not a handy man but this makes you feel like one when it’s accomplished.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I’ve mounted TVs on my walls before but didn’t feel like dealing with finding studs and my friend was borrowing my drill so I found this. I am thoroughly impressed. It holds my 32” perfectly. I was extremely hesitant and nervous I was going to wake up in the middle of the night with my TV crashing down to the floor but it’s been great! Each nail apparently holds 10 pounds and there’s about 15-20 of them. Couldn’t recommend enough. *Note: you can’t turn your tv at all so if you don’t mind that then this will be perfect for your needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good product, one use only.
reviews.reviewText: I installed this product on the wall for a few people. It’s great and fairly easy to install, but if you think you can remove it and use it again think twice. It’s only good for one use as it will be damaged as you try to remove it.

reviews.reviewText: These were dead simple to hang up and align. The built in level was....... adequate. I used a bar level instead. The nail spacing and length insuring a stud hit was a nice touch.

reviews.reviewTitle: マンションの石膏ボードに最適
reviews.reviewText: 石膏ボードに釘を打ちつけて固定する仕様ですが、3センチほどの釘を10本ほど斜めに打ち付けるため、強度の不安も全くありません。また、備えつける壁の裏側も、隣の部屋の壁になっており、壁と壁の厚さは5センチほどしかありませんか、釘後が貫通したり干渉することもありませんでした。装着したテレビは、40型のREGZAですが、付属のネジもピッタリでした。落下を防止のためのワイヤーが独特な形状で、説明書きも不足ですが、なんとか設置しました。
